## SayHello
The macro is [[SayHello]] and we can call it with parameters:
* `{{SayHello|Jack}}`: {{SayHello|Jack}}
* `{{SayHello}}`: {{SayHello}}

## SayHelloAdvanced
The macro is [[SayHelloAdvanced]] and we can call it with named parameters:
* `{{SayHelloAdvanced|name:"Marc"}}`: {{SayHelloAdvanced|name:"Marc" site:"Twikki"}}
* `{{SayHelloAdvanced}}`: {{SayHelloAdvanced}}

